              <p data-wow-delay="0.2s" class="wow fadeInUp">
                Coach Anton Soler founded BODYBYALS during the pandemic, but his journey started long before that.
                Growing up, he was a fat kid and struggled with weight, even though he was active in sports. He realized
                that being active alone wasn’t enough to get results, which sparked his interest in fitness and
                nutrition.<br /><br />
                Over the years, he tried different methods and learned from every experience. All of this taught him that
                lasting results come from controlling hormones and building sustainable habits, rather than just counting
                calories.<br /><br />
                Every day, his vision guides you through BODYBYALS Online Coaching with easy-to-follow workouts, a sustainable
                Nutrition Guide, and healthier carb alternatives like BODYBYALS Shirataki Rice and Keto Bread to support your
                fitness journey.<br /><br />
                Our approach is designed to be sustainable for every client, helping you stay on track while enjoying your
                favorite meals. No matter where you are in your day or your journey, your progress is our mission. Together,
                we’ll help you build healthier habits and turn your wellness goals into reality.
